I hope I can wash this off.

228
00:18:49,002 --> 00:18:50,422
Heâ¦

229
00:18:50,504 --> 00:18:52,804
He is angrier than he was
when I told him I decided

230
00:18:52,881 --> 00:18:54,511
to stop training with chaste herbs.

231
00:18:57,094 --> 00:19:00,934
Wait. He got that scarf
from Maidservant Kim.

232
00:19:15,779 --> 00:19:16,949
I am sorry.

233
00:19:21,702 --> 00:19:24,202
We must finish cleaning

234
00:19:24,288 --> 00:19:26,618
before the mages begin their day,
so move quickly.

235
00:19:26,707 --> 00:19:27,537
-Yes, ma'am.
-Yes, ma'am.

236
00:19:48,645 --> 00:19:49,935
Where is Young Master Jang?

237
00:19:50,022 --> 00:19:52,072
-Is he not here?
-Wellâ¦

238
00:19:52,149 --> 00:19:53,399
I went to wake him up,

239
00:19:53,483 --> 00:19:55,743
but he told me
he did not sleep a wink last night.

240
00:19:55,819 --> 00:19:58,069
So he did not wake up? On his first day?

241
00:19:59,907 --> 00:20:01,157
See you later, Mu-deok.

242
00:20:18,926 --> 00:20:20,006
Young Master.

243
00:20:20,093 --> 00:20:21,553
You must wake up.

244
00:20:23,263 --> 00:20:24,433
Young Master!

245
00:20:28,143 --> 00:20:29,523
Get up.

246
00:20:29,603 --> 00:20:31,023
Or else I will beat you.

247
00:20:31,104 --> 00:20:32,274
Wake up!

248
00:20:41,531 --> 00:20:43,831
Stop being annoying and go.
I am going to sleep.

249
00:20:46,203 --> 00:20:48,663
Are you out of your mind?
Do you have a death wish?

250
00:20:51,375 --> 00:20:53,035
Yes, I would rather die.

251
00:20:53,752 --> 00:20:55,752
What is the matter with you?

252
00:20:55,837 --> 00:20:58,377
This is just a symptom.
I have been poisoned.

253
00:20:59,716 --> 00:21:02,676
Uk, stop being stubborn with your spite.

254
00:21:05,138 --> 00:21:06,718
I told you I was your antidote.

255
00:21:08,225 --> 00:21:09,055
Here.

256
00:21:10,143 --> 00:21:12,103
Here is your antidote.

257
00:21:23,573 --> 00:21:24,833
I am sorry.

258
00:21:39,298 --> 00:21:40,338
Hey, Uk.

259
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:44,090
I heard you read Words of the Heart.
I am impressed.

260
00:21:44,177 --> 00:21:45,847
It is nothing to be impressed about.

261
00:21:45,929 --> 00:21:48,269
I see you are reading about
the Hyeongong Technique.

262
00:21:48,348 --> 00:21:50,558
I mastered that swordsmanship
when I was little.

263
00:21:51,685 --> 00:21:54,015
If you teach me how to read
Words of the Heart,

264
00:21:54,104 --> 00:21:55,814
I will teach you the Hyeongong Technique.

265
00:21:58,525 --> 00:21:59,355
I am not sure.

266
00:22:01,945 --> 00:22:04,065
Do it. Tell him you will do it.

267
00:22:05,741 --> 00:22:08,161
Listen. I am a bit tired.

268
00:22:09,453 --> 00:22:12,503
You can ask Master Lee
how to read Words of the Heart.

269
00:22:21,340 --> 00:22:22,380
Uk.

270
00:22:23,091 --> 00:22:25,551
I mastered Ryusu
around the same time you did.

271
00:22:26,178 --> 00:22:29,058
So what do you say we fight a duel?

272
00:22:29,139 --> 00:22:31,429
Then I will lend you
a precious sapphire mat

273
00:22:31,516 --> 00:22:33,476
that I use for training.

274
00:22:34,519 --> 00:22:37,229
If you train with that,
it will double your energy.

275
00:22:37,314 --> 00:22:40,614
A sapphire mat?
That is very hard to come by.

276
00:22:42,027 --> 00:22:43,897
Young Master, this is great.

277
00:22:46,239 --> 00:22:48,579
But sapphire mats are really cold,
are they not?

278
00:22:49,367 --> 00:22:51,287
I easily get cold these days.

279
00:22:52,370 --> 00:22:54,410
So I do not need something like that.

280
00:23:02,547 --> 00:23:03,837
What are you doing?

281
00:23:05,217 --> 00:23:08,847
I have not been sleeping well these days,
so I am going to take a nap.

282
00:23:10,597 --> 00:23:13,727
You missed your chance
to learn the Hyeongong Technique.

283
00:23:13,809 --> 00:23:14,809
Are you mad?

284
00:23:14,893 --> 00:23:17,653
The same goes for yesterday.
Sapphire mats are so rare,

285
00:23:17,729 --> 00:23:19,149
but you refused, saying it was cold.

286
00:23:19,231 --> 00:23:21,781
You should have said yes
even if you were to die on that mat.

287
00:23:21,858 --> 00:23:24,488
You are unbelievable.
"You are mad. Just die."

288
00:23:24,569 --> 00:23:26,399
That is all you ever say to me.

289
00:23:28,281 --> 00:23:29,701
Just give me that.

290
00:23:39,835 --> 00:23:40,745
What are you doing?

291
00:23:40,836 --> 00:23:42,376
There is no space to nap together.

292
00:23:43,296 --> 00:23:45,126
You must get through me to take a nap.

293
00:23:48,802 --> 00:23:49,972
Move.

294
00:23:51,054 --> 00:23:52,224
Make me.

295
00:23:52,305 --> 00:23:55,175
It will not take too much effort.

296
00:23:59,479 --> 00:24:00,939
Damn it.

297
00:24:09,281 --> 00:24:11,071
I told you I missed you,

298
00:24:11,158 --> 00:24:14,738
but you told me I was poisoned.
I need to sleep to recover from the shock,

299
00:24:14,828 --> 00:24:16,828
so stop pushing me
and stay away for a bit.

300
00:24:20,959 --> 00:24:23,629
You just want to make me feel frustrated.

301
00:24:25,005 --> 00:24:27,085
Like I said, if I die, you die.

302
00:24:27,883 --> 00:24:30,643
I am in agony,
so you should at least feel irritated.

303
00:24:30,719 --> 00:24:33,889
I even have convulsions
when I sleep these days.

304
00:24:40,353 --> 00:24:41,813
For how long, then?

305
00:24:43,023 --> 00:24:43,863
I do not know.

306
00:24:44,482 --> 00:24:46,112
Why? Does it frustrate you?

307
00:24:46,735 --> 00:24:48,395
That will help me sleep well.

308
00:24:57,621 --> 00:25:01,541
Young Master Jang will not stop sleeping.

309
00:25:01,625 --> 00:25:04,085
You should beat him up and make him train.

310
00:25:04,169 --> 00:25:06,049
The mages of Jeongjingak train
on their own accord.

311
00:25:06,129 --> 00:25:09,219
How fast one masters one's energy
all depends on the individual.

312
00:25:09,299 --> 00:25:11,679
I will not interfere
as long as he sticks to the rules.

313
00:25:13,094 --> 00:25:14,014
Butâ¦

314
00:25:14,095 --> 00:25:16,465
Do not worry. There he is.

315
00:25:18,934 --> 00:25:20,064
Hello.

316
00:25:22,479 --> 00:25:25,149
My head hurts so much.

317
00:25:25,232 --> 00:25:26,522
I would like to go home

318
00:25:26,608 --> 00:25:29,108
and recuperate by taking a bath.

319
00:25:31,321 --> 00:25:33,661
Why does your heart hurt?
You have not done a thing.

320
00:25:34,241 --> 00:25:37,241
You cannot go home on your own accord.
That is against the rules.

321
00:25:37,327 --> 00:25:38,407
Is it not?

322
00:25:38,495 --> 00:25:41,155
Uk is an exception.
The leader gave him permission.

323
00:25:41,748 --> 00:25:42,708
Why only him?

324
00:25:42,791 --> 00:25:45,791
You may have been too busy
having fun to know about this,

325
00:25:45,877 --> 00:25:48,797
but I made a deal with the leader
while I was locked in here.

326
00:25:51,591 --> 00:25:52,591
I will be back.

327
00:25:57,055 --> 00:25:58,595
I will go with him.

328
00:26:00,058 --> 00:26:01,978
If you go, you will be fired.

329
00:26:02,060 --> 00:26:05,360
You went through a lot to get hired.
Are you okay with getting fired?

330
00:26:10,694 --> 00:26:11,654
Damn it.

331
00:26:15,991 --> 00:26:18,081
Jang Uk went home.

332
00:26:18,159 --> 00:26:19,659
Are you sure that is okay?

333
00:26:19,744 --> 00:26:23,084
Let him do whatever he wants

334
00:26:24,791 --> 00:26:26,501
so he can remain lazy.

335
00:26:27,127 --> 00:26:27,997
My lord.

336
00:26:31,965 --> 00:26:34,465
Lady Jin is asking you
to wait a little longer.

337
00:26:35,302 --> 00:26:38,222
Is she with another guest?

338
00:26:44,394 --> 00:26:47,154
I saw a servant from Cheonbugwan
on our way inside.

339
00:26:47,230 --> 00:26:50,320
By any chance, do you think
Assistant Gwanju Jin Mu is here?

340
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:54,990
They are not close enough
to personally meet up like this.

341
00:26:56,156 --> 00:26:59,656
Just in case, go see if anyone leaves.

342
00:27:10,837 --> 00:27:12,457
If that is what Master Lee wants,

343
00:27:12,547 --> 00:27:15,587
we will store Words of the Heart
safely in Jinyowon.

344
00:27:17,344 --> 00:27:20,314
Were you meeting someone else before me?

345
00:27:21,181 --> 00:27:22,641
A distant relative.

346
00:27:24,809 --> 00:27:29,059
Is Young Lady Jin going to be
the official heir of Jinyowon?

347
00:27:31,066 --> 00:27:32,526
That has not been decided yet.

348
00:27:33,401 --> 00:27:35,821
My eldest daughter might still be alive.

349
00:27:38,031 --> 00:27:40,241
It has been ten years since the accident.

350
00:27:41,451 --> 00:27:43,371
Although she could not see,

351
00:27:43,453 --> 00:27:47,423
she could feel energy
and could control relics like no other.

352
00:27:47,499 --> 00:27:49,209
She was a very clever girl.

353
00:27:49,292 --> 00:27:50,712
Unlike other babies,

354
00:27:51,628 --> 00:27:54,918
it took her 13 months
to come out into this world.

355
00:27:56,466 --> 00:27:59,926
She was born on the very day
that Gwanju Jang Gang picked

356
00:28:00,011 --> 00:28:01,471
as a blessed day from the skies.

357
00:28:03,723 --> 00:28:07,483
She was born exactly on the day
that Jang Gang picked for you?

358
00:28:08,937 --> 00:28:10,107
Is it possible

359
00:28:10,188 --> 00:28:14,228
to choose the date and time
of a baby's birth?

360
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,900
It just happened to match.

361
00:28:18,571 --> 00:28:21,911
I would like to invite Master Lee
to Jinyowon someday.

362
00:28:22,492 --> 00:28:23,792
Please tell him that.

363
00:28:25,036 --> 00:28:26,116
I will.

364
00:28:41,886 --> 00:28:43,926
I had her inside me for 13 months.

365
00:28:44,013 --> 00:28:47,063
I cannot let her go like this.

366
00:28:48,685 --> 00:28:50,555
I heard the ice stone has the power

367
00:28:50,645 --> 00:28:53,565
to bring back the souls of the dead.

368
00:29:00,196 --> 00:29:01,316
Gwanju.

369
00:29:03,366 --> 00:29:04,576
Please help me.

370
00:29:14,878 --> 00:29:19,508
I went far and beyond to protect my baby.

371
00:29:30,852 --> 00:29:32,102
I will find you.

372
00:29:34,522 --> 00:29:36,692
I will do everything I can

373
00:29:38,526 --> 00:29:39,856
to find you.

374
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:54,830
-Did you check who the previous guest was?
-Yes.

375
00:29:56,377 --> 00:29:59,837
It was Assistant Gwanju Jin Mu.

376
00:30:02,175 --> 00:30:04,295
Since when did the leader of Jinyowon

377
00:30:04,385 --> 00:30:07,635
acknowledge him as a family member
and meet with him like this?

378
00:30:07,722 --> 00:30:09,562
He quietly left through the back gate.

379
00:30:10,308 --> 00:30:13,018
They must have made a secret deal.

380
00:30:14,187 --> 00:30:16,897
I wonder what that cunning man, Jin Mu,

381
00:30:16,981 --> 00:30:19,941
is using as bait
to freely enter Jinyowon like this.

382
00:30:37,293 --> 00:30:40,673
There is no way to find out where you are
since you cannot see.

383
00:30:41,798 --> 00:30:44,798
If you do as you are told
and stay completely silent,

384
00:30:45,385 --> 00:30:46,925
your life will be spared.

385
00:30:47,554 --> 00:30:49,394
Do not make any noise.

386
00:30:49,472 --> 00:30:50,562
Stand up.

387
00:32:10,887 --> 00:32:12,057
Sit down.

388
00:32:20,313 --> 00:32:22,943
Leave that one here. The others can go.

389
00:32:26,486 --> 00:32:28,736
They are looking for the girl
in the portrait.

390
00:32:28,821 --> 00:32:30,321
She must be blind.

391
00:32:31,366 --> 00:32:34,326
He just said the others could leave,
but why is there no movement?

392
00:33:03,898 --> 00:33:05,398
You can see.

393
00:33:07,986 --> 00:33:10,906
What a pity.
I thought I had found an adequate girl.

394
00:33:11,447 --> 00:33:12,367
Kill her.

395
00:33:16,244 --> 00:33:17,874
I can do it!

396
00:33:19,747 --> 00:33:23,327
I can be the girl in the portrait.

397
00:33:29,298 --> 00:33:30,508
Please have mercy.

398
00:33:31,217 --> 00:33:32,887
You said I was adequate.

399
00:33:34,095 --> 00:33:35,965
If you need me to be blindâ¦

400
00:33:39,100 --> 00:33:41,190
then blind I will be.

401
00:33:55,783 --> 00:33:59,003
You are a very daring girl. Stand up.

402
00:34:04,917 --> 00:34:07,087
So you can act like you are blind?

403
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,590
I already am blind.

404
00:34:13,134 --> 00:34:15,604
Let me see if that is true.

405
00:34:53,966 --> 00:34:56,796
It really looks like
I have found an adequate girl.

406
00:35:16,405 --> 00:35:17,865
You will do.

407
00:35:17,949 --> 00:35:21,949
From now on, you are Jin Bu-yeon,
the missing daughter of Jinyowon.

408
00:35:23,079 --> 00:35:24,119
Yes.

409
00:35:25,289 --> 00:35:27,129
I am Jin Bu-yeon.

410
00:35:39,303 --> 00:35:41,313
Uk has stopped once again.

411
00:35:45,768 --> 00:35:49,268
What kind of cliff
do I have to push him off of this time?

412
00:35:54,569 --> 00:35:56,739
I see you are working hard thanks to me.

413
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,120
Yes.

414
00:36:02,702 --> 00:36:05,962
Thanks to you,
I will have to sweep the yard again.

415
00:36:13,379 --> 00:36:14,629
Are you complaining?

416
00:36:15,673 --> 00:36:16,843
Then I will have you gone.

417
00:36:16,924 --> 00:36:18,264
You cheated your way in here.

418
00:36:18,801 --> 00:36:20,931
If I say a word about this,
you will be fired.

419
00:36:23,222 --> 00:36:24,812
Forgive me, Your Royal Highness.

420
00:36:25,892 --> 00:36:28,982
I am grateful for the leaves
you have sprinkled for me to sweep.

421
00:36:29,061 --> 00:36:31,611
You may keep going your way,
Your Royal Highness.

422
00:36:33,399 --> 00:36:35,069
You should be grateful

423
00:36:36,027 --> 00:36:38,487
for the answer sheet I gave you,
not these leaves.

424
00:36:40,531 --> 00:36:45,451
I see you were not being grouchy.
You just wanted to receive credit.

425
00:36:45,536 --> 00:36:48,246
Goodness, I was too slow to notice that.

426
00:36:48,331 --> 00:36:50,251
I am grateful, Your Royal Highness.

427
00:36:51,042 --> 00:36:54,132
Of course, you are grateful.
I solved those questions myself.

428
00:36:55,671 --> 00:36:58,091
Do you even know
how to wash off ink stains?

429
00:36:59,467 --> 00:37:02,597
You solved that question,
Your Royal Highness?

430
00:37:03,221 --> 00:37:06,021
Yes, that is right. I am the Crown Prince.

431
00:37:06,098 --> 00:37:08,598
Yet I learned that rice paste
gets rid of ink stains.

432
00:37:09,227 --> 00:37:12,307
I even tried it myself,
and it actually worked.

433
00:37:13,022 --> 00:37:14,402
Unbelievable.

434
00:37:15,983 --> 00:37:18,113
I am forever indebted to you.

435
00:37:19,695 --> 00:37:20,815
So tell me.

436
00:37:21,739 --> 00:37:23,239
Are you happy to be with your master?

437
00:37:24,659 --> 00:37:26,289
I heard Uk read Words of the Heart.

438
00:37:26,369 --> 00:37:27,499
Yes.

439
00:37:27,578 --> 00:37:30,958
He was the fastest mage
in Jeongjingak to have read it.

440
00:37:34,085 --> 00:37:35,995
I doubt he read it with his skills.

441
00:37:36,587 --> 00:37:38,257
He probably got lucky again.

442
00:37:39,298 --> 00:37:42,088
But still, he beat you in a duel.

443
00:37:42,677 --> 00:37:43,677
Goodness.

444
00:37:45,304 --> 00:37:48,934
I know Uk's level of capacity very well
since I have fought against him.

445
00:37:50,309 --> 00:37:53,099
He has bad swordsmanship,
and his spells are weak.

446
00:37:53,187 --> 00:37:56,897
He got lucky and beat me by using Tansu.
It was not because he was skilled.

447
00:37:58,192 --> 00:38:00,242
He is accurate.

448
00:38:00,987 --> 00:38:04,617
That is why he came to Jeongjingak.
To become a mage of a higher level.

449
00:38:04,699 --> 00:38:07,829
To be frank, he does not even have
what it takes to enter Jeongjingak.

450
00:38:08,494 --> 00:38:11,914
If he manages to beat anyone here,

451
00:38:12,665 --> 00:38:14,285
then I shall acknowledge him.

452
00:38:15,584 --> 00:38:18,634
Using the Crown Prince
would not be such a bad idea.

453
00:38:18,713 --> 00:38:19,803
Your Royal Highness.

454
00:38:20,339 --> 00:38:23,719
Then how about we make a bet?

455
00:38:24,552 --> 00:38:25,722
A bet?

456
00:38:27,054 --> 00:38:29,184
What will I gain
from making a bet with you?

457
00:38:30,391 --> 00:38:34,231
I will bet the most precious thing I own.

458
00:38:42,486 --> 00:38:43,856
I will choose first.

459
00:38:43,946 --> 00:38:45,816
I pick red. You can have the blue one.

460
00:38:51,037 --> 00:38:53,827
Wait there. I will go to you soon.

461
00:38:54,498 --> 00:38:55,878
I also missed you.

462
00:38:57,335 --> 00:38:58,665
That is my reply.

463
00:39:08,763 --> 00:39:10,393
-Young Master.
-Hey.

464
00:39:11,015 --> 00:39:13,095
I brought honey biscuits, your favorite.

465
00:39:13,934 --> 00:39:15,394
Are you also staying for dinner?

466
00:39:15,478 --> 00:39:17,478
No, I am staying here for a few days.

467
00:39:18,439 --> 00:39:21,649
-Is that allowed?
-The leader gave me his permission.

468
00:39:21,734 --> 00:39:23,994
He let me be an exception for everything.

469
00:39:24,070 --> 00:39:25,360
Well, I get why.

470
00:39:25,446 --> 00:39:28,196
It only took you a few days
to read Words of the Heart.

471
00:39:28,282 --> 00:39:31,452
It is absurd to make you abide
by the same rules as ordinary mages.

472
00:39:32,495 --> 00:39:34,905
Are you happy about my achievements?

473
00:39:34,997 --> 00:39:36,827
I am more than happy.

474
00:39:36,916 --> 00:39:39,206
You have no idea how proud I am.

475
00:39:41,045 --> 00:39:42,455
Maidservant Kim.

476
00:39:42,546 --> 00:39:46,176
I know I have always disappointed you,
but you can feel proud now.

477
00:39:46,258 --> 00:39:49,098
Should I get you a nice dress
to help you boast?

478
00:39:49,178 --> 00:39:50,598
My goodness.

479
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:54,729
I do not wish for anything anymore.
I already feel like I have everything.

480
00:39:55,976 --> 00:39:57,436
These days, people come up to me

481
00:39:57,520 --> 00:40:00,940
and tell me that
you truly are your father's son.

482
00:40:02,775 --> 00:40:03,775
They do?

483
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,650
Your father used to be called a genius,

484
00:40:06,737 --> 00:40:10,237
and they say you are
as talented as your father.

485
00:40:12,243 --> 00:40:14,623
People used to say I was nothing like him.

486
00:40:17,998 --> 00:40:19,628
As you continue to achieve things,

487
00:40:20,292 --> 00:40:23,962
there will be fewer people
who say that about you.

488
00:40:24,046 --> 00:40:27,216
What if I do not do well?
Will they say I am not his son again?

489
00:40:29,093 --> 00:40:30,223
No, that is notâ¦

490
00:40:31,554 --> 00:40:34,644
Tell them to go ahead
and say what they want about me.

491
00:40:34,723 --> 00:40:36,023
I do not care anymore.

492
00:40:37,059 --> 00:40:39,899
Yes, we should not
let that bother us anymore.

493
00:40:41,939 --> 00:40:46,899
Frankly speaking, you are responsible
for your own achievements.

494
00:40:46,986 --> 00:40:48,356
Your father is irrelevant.

495
00:40:49,071 --> 00:40:51,451
He was never around for you anyway.

496
00:40:52,032 --> 00:40:55,702
And to be honest, it is all because

497
00:40:55,786 --> 00:40:57,156
I raised you well.

498
00:41:03,961 --> 00:41:07,011
You will always be
my precious young master

499
00:41:07,923 --> 00:41:10,553
no matter how competent
or incompetent you are.

500
00:41:12,011 --> 00:41:13,051
Really?

501
00:41:14,555 --> 00:41:18,055
Then can I go back
to slacking off like I used to?

502
00:41:19,810 --> 00:41:21,770
Yes, if that is what you want.

503
00:41:22,563 --> 00:41:25,023
But I thought you hated that.

504
00:41:26,567 --> 00:41:30,237
Compared to the times
when you used to slack off at home,

505
00:41:30,321 --> 00:41:33,531
you looked a lot happier
when you had just come back

506
00:41:34,533 --> 00:41:36,163
from your training in Danhyanggok.

507
00:41:37,495 --> 00:41:40,405
That is why I could not stop you
even though it seemed dangerous.

508
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:42,080
You see,

509
00:41:42,625 --> 00:41:47,415
I want you to achieve
everything you want to achieve.

510
00:41:50,049 --> 00:41:51,179
All right.

511
00:41:55,179 --> 00:41:56,509
I should go back.

512
00:41:57,598 --> 00:41:59,268
You are leaving?

513
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:02,900
Yes. If you forced me to leave,
then I would have refused to go.

514
00:42:02,978 --> 00:42:05,058
But after that speech,
I should go and study.

515
00:42:05,147 --> 00:42:08,777
I should do everything I can
to make you proud, Maidservant Kim.

516
00:42:10,236 --> 00:42:12,526
How is your headache? Is it better?

517
00:42:13,239 --> 00:42:14,369
Yes.

518
00:42:15,241 --> 00:42:17,241
Horses and people are trained

519
00:42:17,326 --> 00:42:19,576
through the carrot-and-stick approach.

520
00:42:20,788 --> 00:42:23,868
But recently,
I kept getting hit by a stick.

521
00:42:24,458 --> 00:42:27,338
Who in the world dared to hit you?

522
00:42:27,419 --> 00:42:29,879
Do not worry. I am not one
to stay still after getting beaten.

523
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,340
Just pack me some snacks.

524
00:42:33,425 --> 00:42:34,835
A ton of honey biscuits.

525
00:42:35,803 --> 00:42:38,513
-This is going to be fun.
-Are you sure?

526
00:42:39,598 --> 00:42:40,678
Hey, Uk.

527
00:42:41,976 --> 00:42:43,096
You are finally here.

528
00:42:43,811 --> 00:42:44,941
Yes.

529
00:42:45,020 --> 00:42:47,820
Why does it seem like
you have all been waiting for me?

530
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:50,900
Are you fans of the honey biscuits
I bring from home?

531
00:42:50,985 --> 00:42:54,065
You should go to the Training Center.
It will be fun.

532
00:43:05,541 --> 00:43:07,631
-You have been waiting for me?
-Yes.

533
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:10,460
I will be your first opponent.

534
00:43:11,964 --> 00:43:12,804
What?

535
00:43:13,549 --> 00:43:15,339
Let us fight a duel.

536
00:43:16,093 --> 00:43:18,143
If you refuse, you lose.

537
00:43:19,013 --> 00:43:20,473
What are you talking about?

538
00:43:24,476 --> 00:43:26,096
Just take it.

539
00:43:55,633 --> 00:43:56,723
Uk has lost.

540
00:43:58,510 --> 00:44:01,430
Gu Hyo, the winner,
may take the first gold toad.

541
00:44:29,291 --> 00:44:30,671
What is going on?

542
00:44:30,751 --> 00:44:32,001
I have made a bet.

543
00:44:32,086 --> 00:44:34,376
I never made a bet with you,
Your Royal Highness.

544
00:44:34,463 --> 00:44:37,223
Not with you. I have made a bet
with your maid, Mu-deok.

545
00:44:41,303 --> 00:44:44,523
I told her that you did not
have the skills to beat any of the mages

546
00:44:44,598 --> 00:44:45,968
here at Jeongjingak.

547
00:44:46,058 --> 00:44:49,058
But your maid insisted that
you could at least beat one.

548
00:44:49,978 --> 00:44:51,808
Mu-deok said that, did she?

549
00:44:53,774 --> 00:44:56,114
You will fight a duel every day
for ten days.

550
00:44:56,193 --> 00:44:58,033
If you fail to beat a single fight,

551
00:44:58,112 --> 00:45:00,572
she will give me an item
that is most valuable to her.

552
00:45:02,282 --> 00:45:03,372
Valuable?

553
00:45:04,535 --> 00:45:06,245
What valuable item do you have?

554
00:45:06,870 --> 00:45:08,620
It is something you gave me.

555
00:45:10,707 --> 00:45:12,167
This is what she bet.

556
00:45:21,677 --> 00:45:24,297
This jade looks very valuable,
so I want it for myself.

557
00:45:26,515 --> 00:45:28,305
So I brought gold toads

558
00:45:28,392 --> 00:45:29,982
as prizes for the match.

559
00:45:36,650 --> 00:45:40,450
If you fail to beat a single opponent
before all those toads disappear,

560
00:45:40,529 --> 00:45:41,949
this will be mine.

561
00:45:42,573 --> 00:45:44,833
I am not interested
in taking part in this bet.

562
00:45:45,659 --> 00:45:48,409
This is not a bet between us.
It is a bet I made with her.

563
00:45:50,164 --> 00:45:51,504
If you give up,

564
00:45:51,582 --> 00:45:54,082
you will not have won a single match,
so she will lose.

565
00:45:54,960 --> 00:45:56,090
And this will be mine.

566
00:46:00,799 --> 00:46:01,929
Young Master Jang.

567
00:46:03,177 --> 00:46:05,847
That is the most precious object
I have ever received.

568
00:46:07,806 --> 00:46:11,306
Please do your best
so you can win it back.

569
00:46:22,446 --> 00:46:23,486
Look at that.

570
00:46:24,114 --> 00:46:25,744
You really won this gold toad.

571
00:46:25,824 --> 00:46:29,374
Of course. Uk may have managed
to read Words of the Heart,

572
00:46:29,453 --> 00:46:31,793
-but he is a bad swordsman.
-What is going on?

573
00:46:33,707 --> 00:46:36,537
The Crown Prince and Mu-deok
made a bet over Uk.

574
00:46:37,544 --> 00:46:40,844
The Crown Prince brought gold toads,
so everyone is eager to participate.

575
00:46:42,257 --> 00:46:45,177
The strongest mages
are lining up to fight Uk.

576
00:46:47,179 --> 00:46:48,809
Put it down.

577
00:46:56,230 --> 00:46:58,730
The Crown Prince mocked your competence.

578
00:46:59,274 --> 00:47:01,284
As your master, I could not let it slide.

579
00:47:01,360 --> 00:47:04,280
Do not lie to me. I know you.

580
00:47:05,531 --> 00:47:07,241
I have been lazy these past few days,

581
00:47:07,324 --> 00:47:09,704
so you made that senseless bet
to force me to train.

582
00:47:12,204 --> 00:47:13,124
Yes, I did.

583
00:47:14,665 --> 00:47:18,955
You will have to fight ten mages
regardless of your will.

584
00:47:20,462 --> 00:47:23,632
The first duel was
incredibly disappointing.

585
00:47:24,258 --> 00:47:26,338
Your sword was slow,
and your feet were heavy.

586
00:47:26,426 --> 00:47:29,676
-Tomorrow's opponent is from the Jung--
-I am not doing it.

587
00:47:32,975 --> 00:47:35,265
Even if you lose,
you always memorize what you see,

588
00:47:35,352 --> 00:47:36,562
so it will help you learn.

589
00:47:36,645 --> 00:47:39,645
-I told you I am not fighting.
-As you fight ten mages,

590
00:47:39,731 --> 00:47:42,231
you will learn ten different spells.

591
00:47:43,068 --> 00:47:44,568
-Mu-deok--
-Young Master.

592
00:47:44,653 --> 00:47:46,823
Feel free to go home
for a bath again tomorrow.

593
00:47:46,905 --> 00:47:49,195
Then you will never get that jade back.

594
00:47:50,784 --> 00:47:51,914
All right, fine.

595
00:47:52,953 --> 00:47:54,543
So you made this bet.

596
00:47:55,122 --> 00:47:56,122
Butâ¦

597
00:47:57,291 --> 00:47:59,001
But how could you bet on that?

598
00:47:59,710 --> 00:48:00,840
You know why.

599
00:48:01,336 --> 00:48:04,796
That was the only thing
to motivate you to fight hard and win.

600
00:48:07,551 --> 00:48:08,721
When I said I missed you,

601
00:48:08,802 --> 00:48:11,352
is this what you meant
when you said you had my weakness?

602
00:48:14,182 --> 00:48:15,312
Yes.

603
00:48:16,685 --> 00:48:18,475
You probably despise me right now,

604
00:48:19,688 --> 00:48:22,518
but you cannot lose
what we share to someone else.

605
00:48:27,321 --> 00:48:29,621
So this is why you said I was poisoned.

606
00:48:29,698 --> 00:48:31,988
If you get it back,
I will give you a bright smile.

607
00:48:32,909 --> 00:48:34,289
Just like an antidote.

608
00:48:38,790 --> 00:48:39,920
Uk.

609
00:48:41,251 --> 00:48:42,751
Return it to me no matter what.

610
00:48:43,837 --> 00:48:46,207
It is the most precious item
I have ever received

611
00:48:47,674 --> 00:48:49,304
in my entire life.

612
00:48:52,012 --> 00:48:53,562
Is it really precious to you?

613
00:48:54,431 --> 00:48:55,681
Do you not want it back

614
00:48:57,142 --> 00:48:58,642
merely because of its price?

615
00:49:04,191 --> 00:49:06,231
I will get it back from the Crown Prince.

616
00:49:07,152 --> 00:49:09,202
It would be funny to share
that jade with him.

617
00:49:16,244 --> 00:49:18,504
But it was not worth
sharing it with you either.

618
00:49:40,352 --> 00:49:42,982
I heard you have been
visiting Sejukwon pretty often.

619
00:49:43,605 --> 00:49:46,815
Is it because you wish
to appoint Master Heo as your master

620
00:49:47,401 --> 00:49:49,651
and learn spells from him?

621
00:49:50,946 --> 00:49:52,156
Do not be ridiculous.

622
00:49:52,906 --> 00:49:54,736
You are my master.

623
00:49:55,826 --> 00:49:57,576
I am only going there for treatment.

624
00:49:57,661 --> 00:50:01,291
It allows me to get some fresh air.
Not to mention, fun things happen there.

625
00:50:01,373 --> 00:50:05,043
You must enjoy hanging out
with the mages of Songrim.

626
00:50:05,127 --> 00:50:07,297
I get to meet Yul, my cousin.

627
00:50:07,379 --> 00:50:09,549
Park Dang-gu is
a lively person to be around.

628
00:50:09,631 --> 00:50:12,881
As for Jang Uk, I would like
to teach him a lesson, but it is not easy.

629
00:50:13,427 --> 00:50:15,967
He seemed elated
after having read Words of the Heart,

630
00:50:16,054 --> 00:50:18,014
so I put him back in his place today.

631
00:50:18,098 --> 00:50:20,598
He lost to a mage who just mastered Ryusu.

632
00:50:20,684 --> 00:50:22,814
So people know his true competence now.

633
00:50:22,894 --> 00:50:24,604
People no longer admire him.

634
00:50:31,611 --> 00:50:32,951
That is a nice jade.

635
00:50:33,655 --> 00:50:35,815
I got it in exchange for ten gold toads.

636
00:50:36,825 --> 00:50:39,615
-Is it something valuable?
-That blue jade holds yin energy.

637
00:50:40,328 --> 00:50:42,248
Where is the other one?

638
00:50:42,330 --> 00:50:43,370
The other one?

639
00:50:43,457 --> 00:50:45,877
Items with opposite energies
come in pairs.

640
00:50:45,959 --> 00:50:48,209
There should be a red jade
that goes with it.

641
00:50:48,962 --> 00:50:51,092
They are only valuable
when they are together.

642
00:50:55,844 --> 00:50:57,604
So this is supposed to be a pair?

643
00:50:58,096 --> 00:50:59,256
Eunuch Oh.

644
00:51:00,056 --> 00:51:02,596
What does it mean when two people
share something that should be a pair?

645
00:51:02,684 --> 00:51:04,774
It means they are married or a couple.

646
00:51:07,230 --> 00:51:08,690
Damn it.

647
00:51:09,316 --> 00:51:12,356
Do you not like the jade,
Your Royal Highness?

648
00:51:12,444 --> 00:51:15,864
I do not like it. It gets on my nerves.
It extremely bothers me.

649
00:51:16,364 --> 00:51:19,284
Take it away and smash it to pieces.

650
00:51:19,367 --> 00:51:21,997
You cannot do that yet.

651
00:51:22,078 --> 00:51:23,748
Jang Uk might win it back.

652
00:51:26,208 --> 00:51:27,998
If he takes it back,

653
00:51:28,877 --> 00:51:30,297
they will become a pair again.

654
00:51:31,713 --> 00:51:32,883
Damn it.

655
00:51:45,185 --> 00:51:46,345
-Master Lee.
-Yesâ¦

656
00:51:49,481 --> 00:51:51,941
What brings you here?

657
00:51:54,277 --> 00:51:56,987
I wore hemp fabric all year round,
yet I never felt cold.

658
00:51:57,823 --> 00:51:58,663
Butâ¦

659
00:51:59,658 --> 00:52:01,368
after I wore this scarf,

660
00:52:02,244 --> 00:52:04,414
I realized how cold it had been.

661
00:52:06,915 --> 00:52:08,535
What is that over there?

662
00:52:11,127 --> 00:52:12,127
Whatâ¦

663
00:52:12,212 --> 00:52:13,052
My goodness.

664
00:52:17,008 --> 00:52:20,678
I never once thought flowers were pretty,

665
00:52:22,097 --> 00:52:25,887
but I saw these flowers
and wanted to show them to you.

666
00:52:33,149 --> 00:52:34,689
How pretty.

667
00:52:35,694 --> 00:52:38,244
Are they for me?

668
00:52:45,662 --> 00:52:48,002
These booksâ¦

669
00:52:48,081 --> 00:52:49,461
You have nice books here.

670
00:52:50,625 --> 00:52:52,375
What a great read.

671
00:52:59,426 --> 00:53:00,926
About Maidservant Kimâ¦

672
00:53:02,012 --> 00:53:03,182
Is she sick?

673
00:53:03,263 --> 00:53:05,313
I have not seen her at Songrim these days.

674
00:53:05,390 --> 00:53:06,930
She went there yesterday.

675
00:53:07,559 --> 00:53:09,639
She goes there often
to meet Young Master Jang.

676
00:53:10,729 --> 00:53:11,899
I see.

677
00:53:14,024 --> 00:53:16,484
She just did not drop by to see me.

678
00:53:18,528 --> 00:53:20,778
She is with a guest right now.

679
00:53:20,864 --> 00:53:22,664
A guest? Who is it?

680
00:53:22,741 --> 00:53:26,161
I do not know who he is,
but he was a young man.

681
00:53:26,953 --> 00:53:28,373
A young man?

682
00:53:29,372 --> 00:53:33,042
From what I know, Maidservant Kim
is not acquainted with any young men.

683
00:53:42,969 --> 00:53:44,599
Maidservant Kim.

684
00:53:50,185 --> 00:53:51,515
Hello.

685
00:53:53,355 --> 00:53:55,065
What are those weeds?

686
00:53:55,148 --> 00:53:56,938
They are flowers.

687
00:53:57,817 --> 00:54:00,027
-How could you call them weeds?
-Maidservant Kim.

688
00:54:00,528 --> 00:54:04,118
Did you get upset that day
because I was a bit harsh?

689
00:54:04,908 --> 00:54:06,408
Is that why you stopped visiting?

690
00:54:07,452 --> 00:54:10,962
I really had no idea.
I thought you were sick.

691
00:54:11,039 --> 00:54:13,079
I came here worried for nothing.

692
00:54:13,166 --> 00:54:14,876
You should not have come.

693
00:54:15,502 --> 00:54:17,592
You said you would never visit again.

694
00:54:17,671 --> 00:54:19,671
When did I ever say that?

695
00:54:19,756 --> 00:54:21,166
You are mistaken.

696
00:54:22,592 --> 00:54:24,182
But still,

697
00:54:24,260 --> 00:54:26,550
I am glad that you are all right.

698
00:54:32,435 --> 00:54:34,595
If you were worried that I might be sick,

699
00:54:35,772 --> 00:54:38,732
you could have brought me
a bundle of weeds like this one.

700
00:54:38,817 --> 00:54:40,647
Do you need weeds?

701
00:54:41,236 --> 00:54:42,356
I will get them for you.

702
00:54:44,114 --> 00:54:45,824
I do not need them.

703
00:54:45,907 --> 00:54:49,907
What I want from you are flowers,
not weeds.

704
00:54:52,038 --> 00:54:53,618
I want you to show me

705
00:54:53,707 --> 00:54:55,287
how much you care

706
00:54:56,376 --> 00:54:58,166
by giving me something beautiful.

707
00:55:04,968 --> 00:55:08,048
We still have a guest here,
so you should go.

708
00:55:09,222 --> 00:55:10,472
Maidservant Kim.

709
00:55:11,307 --> 00:55:12,517
Wellâ¦

710
00:55:13,810 --> 00:55:17,400
Next time you come to Songrim to visit Uk,

711
00:55:19,190 --> 00:55:21,740
I hope you will drop by and visit me too.

712
00:55:24,529 --> 00:55:26,489
Waitâ¦

713
00:55:30,243 --> 00:55:32,003
