715
00:55:36,875 --> 00:55:38,075
Maidservant Kim.

716
00:55:40,336 --> 00:55:41,756
What a cold-hearted woman.

717
00:56:06,613 --> 00:56:09,453
Seeing that his shoes
are smaller than mine,

718
00:56:10,909 --> 00:56:12,789
he must be shorter than I am.

719
00:56:27,634 --> 00:56:29,934
Do you like sweet snacks?

720
00:56:30,011 --> 00:56:30,891
Yes, I do.

721
00:56:37,227 --> 00:56:38,387
It is delicious.

722
00:56:39,646 --> 00:56:41,436
Then here is one moreâ¦

723
00:56:43,399 --> 00:56:44,529
For me.

724
00:56:58,957 --> 00:57:00,997
-How do I look?
-You look pretty.

725
00:57:01,084 --> 00:57:02,754
-Try this.
-Me?

726
00:57:02,836 --> 00:57:03,746
How do I look?

727
00:57:03,837 --> 00:57:05,707
-It should go there.
-I see.

728
00:57:18,768 --> 00:57:22,558
Look. There is a flower shop over there.

729
00:57:23,231 --> 00:57:25,281
You said you needed to buy flowers.

730
00:57:25,358 --> 00:57:28,568
I need to buy flowers
to decorate Bu-yeon's room.

731
00:57:30,071 --> 00:57:33,871
We might really find her this time.

732
00:57:41,207 --> 00:57:44,087
Really? Will Jin Mu find her?

733
00:57:45,545 --> 00:57:47,085
It is still a secret.

734
00:57:48,256 --> 00:57:51,426
I really hope Bu-yeon comes back.

735
00:57:51,509 --> 00:57:55,259
Then you will not be able to become
the leader of Jinyowon.

736
00:57:55,346 --> 00:57:58,556
Instead, I will be free
to marry the man I want to marry.

737
00:57:59,684 --> 00:58:02,944
I will be allowed to marry the man I love.

738
00:58:05,440 --> 00:58:06,770
That is good news.

739
00:58:08,735 --> 00:58:11,275
Then we should hurry up
and end our fake engagement.

740
00:58:11,362 --> 00:58:14,742
Thank you for pretending
to be my fake betrothed.

741
00:58:17,410 --> 00:58:18,870
I never pretended.

742
00:58:20,663 --> 00:58:21,793
My feelings

743
00:58:23,291 --> 00:58:24,751
were sincere.

744
00:58:28,421 --> 00:58:29,841
But you are an heir to Songrim.

745
00:58:29,923 --> 00:58:33,723
How could you think of marrying me
and moving in with my family?

746
00:58:35,011 --> 00:58:36,141
I know.

747
00:58:36,971 --> 00:58:38,681
I guess I was worried for nothing.

748
00:58:38,765 --> 00:58:41,135
I was even getting ready

749
00:58:41,976 --> 00:58:43,436
