750
00:58:45,146 --> 00:58:46,476
Are you serious?

751
00:58:47,315 --> 00:58:50,985
You were willing to give up on
becoming Songrim's heir because of me?

752
00:58:51,069 --> 00:58:53,739
You said you did not want
a loveless marriage.

753
00:58:54,739 --> 00:58:56,619
I figured if I married you,

754
00:58:56,699 --> 00:58:58,829
you would at least marry
a man that loved you.

755
00:59:01,371 --> 00:59:02,541
That is why.

756
00:59:03,748 --> 00:59:07,418
Anyway, you should meet a man
that you have feelings for.

757
00:59:34,362 --> 00:59:36,242
I feel like I haveâ¦

758
00:59:37,949 --> 00:59:39,159
already met him.

759
00:59:45,707 --> 00:59:47,957
If you hold onto me like thisâ¦

760
00:59:52,755 --> 00:59:54,585
I will never give up on you.

761
00:59:55,633 --> 00:59:57,433
