762
00:59:58,720 --> 01:00:00,640
There is no turning back.

763
01:00:10,356 --> 01:00:13,606
I should get you flowers
to properly propose to you.

764
01:00:17,447 --> 01:00:18,657
Let us go.

765
01:00:25,913 --> 01:00:29,583
Send these flowers to the Jang family.

766
01:00:29,667 --> 01:00:32,747
Did someone die in the family?

767
01:00:32,837 --> 01:00:34,877
Why are you sending them
white chrysanthemums?

768
01:00:38,593 --> 01:00:40,683
I almost made a huge mistake.

769
01:00:40,762 --> 01:00:41,802
Right.

770
01:00:43,014 --> 01:00:44,274
Everything from here

771
01:00:45,391 --> 01:00:46,891
to all the way over there.

772
01:00:46,976 --> 01:00:48,476
Send them all.

773
01:00:48,561 --> 01:00:51,151
-All these flowers?
-Yes, send them all.

774
01:00:51,230 --> 01:00:53,900
-I am sure she will like at least one.
-Goodness.

775
01:00:53,983 --> 01:00:56,243
My goodness, thank you so much.

776
01:00:58,905 --> 01:01:01,195
-Which one would you like?
-This one.

777
01:01:01,908 --> 01:01:04,038
I can get you everything if you want.

778
01:01:28,643 --> 01:01:30,693
You are the heir of Songrim.

779
01:01:31,854 --> 01:01:34,234
Why would you court
the future leader of Jinyowon?

780
01:01:34,732 --> 01:01:35,822
What was your plan?

781
01:01:36,484 --> 01:01:39,534
Did you plan to give up your succession
and marry into their family?

782
01:01:39,612 --> 01:01:43,202
Uncle, we are in love with each other.

783
01:01:43,866 --> 01:01:45,906
Up until recently, Young Lady Jin

784
01:01:46,828 --> 01:01:48,288
had feelings for Uk.

785
01:01:48,913 --> 01:01:50,963
That is wrong. She proved it to me today.

786
01:01:51,040 --> 01:01:55,000
Young Lady Jin said she could give up
becoming the leader of Jinyowon for love.

787
01:01:55,086 --> 01:01:56,586
They only have one daughter.

788
01:01:56,671 --> 01:01:58,211
Who will lead Jinyowon then?

789
01:01:58,798 --> 01:02:01,258
That position is supposed to go
to the eldest daughter.

790
01:02:01,342 --> 01:02:04,802
They are receiving help from Cheonbugwan
to help find her missing sister.

791
01:02:06,222 --> 01:02:07,142
What?

792
01:02:07,223 --> 01:02:09,933
Assistant Gwanju Jin Mu
visits them every day for that.

793
01:02:11,644 --> 01:02:12,984
Jin Mu?

794
01:02:14,605 --> 01:02:16,565
I too wish I had another brother

795
01:02:16,649 --> 01:02:19,439
