and become Songrim's heir instead.

796
01:02:20,862 --> 01:02:23,322
This is just a question out of curiosity.

797
01:02:24,115 --> 01:02:27,985
Uncle, is there no chance
that you might have a secret child?

798
01:02:31,914 --> 01:02:32,834
No one?

799
01:02:34,459 --> 01:02:35,629
Not once?

800
01:02:38,171 --> 01:02:39,011
Get out.

801
01:02:40,757 --> 01:02:42,087
I said, get out.

802
01:02:42,175 --> 01:02:43,295
Pardon?

803
01:02:43,384 --> 01:02:44,474
Get out!

804
01:02:46,637 --> 01:02:49,267
It is not too late to have a child now.

805
01:02:49,348 --> 01:02:50,308
Hey.

806
01:02:50,391 --> 01:02:52,231
I mean you are still healthy.

807
01:02:54,145 --> 01:02:56,225
Catch that punk!

808
01:03:00,651 --> 01:03:01,901
Oh, dear.

809
01:03:12,830 --> 01:03:15,170
Why are there so many flowers here?

810
01:03:15,833 --> 01:03:19,173
I tried to cut ties with someone,
and this is how he tries to make up.

811
01:03:20,713 --> 01:03:24,263
I hope you forgive him.
The flowers are so pretty.

812
01:03:26,677 --> 01:03:28,547
You speak such kind words.

813
01:03:29,680 --> 01:03:31,720
Young Master Jang's mother

814
01:03:32,308 --> 01:03:34,768
was also kind just like you.

815
01:03:35,770 --> 01:03:37,100
Young Master Jang is kind too.

816
01:03:39,315 --> 01:03:40,315
He is?

817
01:03:41,692 --> 01:03:45,072
What makes you think he is kind?

818
01:03:47,365 --> 01:03:49,365
When he talked about his mother,

819
01:03:49,450 --> 01:03:51,200
I could feel the warmth

820
01:03:52,245 --> 01:03:53,445
in his eyes.

821
01:03:54,831 --> 01:03:55,671
What?

822
01:03:56,415 --> 01:03:59,415
He spoke to you about his mother?

823
01:04:00,711 --> 01:04:02,551
You two must be very close.

824
01:04:03,756 --> 01:04:05,626
No, not yet.

825
01:04:05,716 --> 01:04:07,716
He is the one who wishes to become close.

826
01:04:07,802 --> 01:04:11,182
Last time,
he kept her busy for four hours.

827
01:04:12,306 --> 01:04:13,216
Is that true?

828
01:04:14,433 --> 01:04:16,233
We just had a chat.

829
01:04:18,688 --> 01:04:21,438
So it really is you. The egret.

830
01:04:22,692 --> 01:04:25,782
Young Master Jang can be blunt
due to his past scars.

831
01:04:25,862 --> 01:04:29,572
But after he opens up to someone,
he is very kind and warm.

832
01:04:31,534 --> 01:04:33,454
I hope you visit often.

833
01:04:33,536 --> 01:04:35,786
Think of this place as your nest.

834
01:04:35,872 --> 01:04:38,292
Feel free to fly in here and visit often.

835
01:04:39,500 --> 01:04:40,670
I will.

836
01:04:47,383 --> 01:04:50,893
Jin Mu is helping Jin Ho-gyeong
find her missing daughter?

837
01:04:50,970 --> 01:04:53,220
It looks like he is
using that as an excuse

838
01:04:53,306 --> 01:04:55,136
to frequently visit Jinyowon.

839
01:04:55,933 --> 01:04:59,813
I guess Jin Mu wants Jinyowon on his side.

840
01:05:01,105 --> 01:05:03,645
If Jin Mu gets his hands on Jinyowon,

841
01:05:04,442 --> 01:05:07,192
he will become powerful enough
to fight against Songrim.

842
01:05:07,278 --> 01:05:08,278
Andâ¦

843
01:05:10,281 --> 01:05:12,661
if he no longer fears Songrim,

844
01:05:14,660 --> 01:05:18,210
