and that what we wish for is inevitable.

896
01:11:23,153 --> 01:11:24,413
When that day comes,

897
01:11:25,531 --> 01:11:27,121
everyone here

898
01:11:27,658 --> 01:11:31,038
will overcome death
and be given eternal life.

899
01:11:54,351 --> 01:11:55,941
Did you witness everything?

900
01:11:58,897 --> 01:11:59,977
Yes.

901
01:12:00,065 --> 01:12:04,485
Your job will be to bring someone here.

902
01:12:05,988 --> 01:12:09,828
Jin Ho-gyeong is going to be your mother,
and I want you to win over her heart.

903
01:12:09,908 --> 01:12:12,748
Then bring her to this place.

904
01:12:14,621 --> 01:12:16,041
Can you do that?

905
01:12:19,793 --> 01:12:20,883
Yes.

906
01:12:30,888 --> 01:12:32,308
You found an adequate match.

907
01:12:33,349 --> 01:12:35,729
If we manage to bring Jin Ho-gyeong here,

908
01:12:37,019 --> 01:12:41,019
it will become easier for us
to reveal the ice stone to the world.

909
01:13:32,658 --> 01:13:34,278
My love, why are you still up?

910
01:13:45,504 --> 01:13:47,464
Jin Mu's power and influence

911
01:13:47,548 --> 01:13:51,718
might be stronger
and more widespread than we think.

912
01:13:52,970 --> 01:13:57,020
The King's Star must have appeared to deal
with the chaos brought by the ice stone.

913
01:13:59,476 --> 01:14:02,096
Are you talking about Uk?

914
01:14:02,187 --> 01:14:05,937
Master Seo Gyeong, who stopped the chaos
brought by the ice stone 200 years ago,

915
01:14:06,024 --> 01:14:08,244
was also born with the energy
of the King's Star.

916
01:14:08,318 --> 01:14:10,108
That King's Star
was created through sorcery.

917
01:14:10,195 --> 01:14:12,065
You cannot compare that
to Master Seo Gyeong.

918
01:14:13,365 --> 01:14:16,195
They are different.
I did not say they were the same.

919
01:14:18,036 --> 01:14:19,706
That is why I am curious.

920
01:14:22,791 --> 01:14:26,921
I am curious to see if this new star
will slowly fade away

921
01:14:28,297 --> 01:14:29,877
or start shining brightly.

922
01:15:08,086 --> 01:15:09,126
Win!

923
01:15:09,213 --> 01:15:11,673
-Nice.
-Great job.

924
01:15:11,757 --> 01:15:12,837
I knew you would win.

925
01:15:55,759 --> 01:15:57,389
I know you use Tansu.

926
01:15:58,136 --> 01:16:00,216
The Crown Prince was unaware,
which is why it worked.

927
01:16:00,305 --> 01:16:03,225
But you used Tansu with water
from a puddle everyone can see.

928
01:16:03,308 --> 01:16:04,518
It was not hard to block.

929
01:16:18,699 --> 01:16:19,949
Win!

930
01:16:21,785 --> 01:16:24,615
-You did great!
-Amazing!

931
01:16:44,057 --> 01:16:46,267
There are only three toads left?

932
01:16:46,351 --> 01:16:47,601
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

933
01:16:48,562 --> 01:16:51,692
Does that mean he has been
fighting nonstop for the past seven days?

934
01:16:51,773 --> 01:16:53,863
It means he continuously lost.

935
01:16:55,360 --> 01:16:58,200
I thought he would stop if he kept losing.

936
01:17:01,074 --> 01:17:03,084
But I guess
he will keep fighting for this.

937
01:17:03,160 --> 01:17:06,710
You were right, Your Royal Highness.
His swordsmanship and spells are weak.

938
01:17:06,788 --> 01:17:08,208
But he keeps fighting

939
01:17:08,290 --> 01:17:10,830
only because he is persistent.

940
01:17:11,335 --> 01:17:14,955
I know it is just a duel, but he has been
fighting Jeongjingak mages every day.

941
01:17:15,047 --> 01:17:16,587
So I bet he is exhausted.

942
01:17:16,673 --> 01:17:19,683
I am sure you will win,
Your Royal Highness.

943
01:17:19,760 --> 01:17:22,720
Even I did not get a chance
to fight with Jeongjingak mages.

944
01:17:22,804 --> 01:17:25,274
But I am letting Jang Uk do that

945
01:17:25,349 --> 01:17:27,599
at the expense of my own gold toads.

946
01:17:27,684 --> 01:17:29,694
Did I get fooled by Filthy Mu-deok?

947
01:17:49,873 --> 01:17:52,793
Fight and perish, Jang Uk.

948
01:18:07,307 --> 01:18:10,227
All the pain that does not kill you

949
01:18:15,190 --> 01:18:18,150
will only make you stronger.

950
01:18:51,560 --> 01:18:53,770
-Uk!
-You must be here for your young master.

951
01:18:53,854 --> 01:18:56,114
Uk may be losing, but he is improving.

952
01:18:57,691 --> 01:18:58,531
Do not go.

953
01:18:58,608 --> 01:19:00,398
Do not go to your room and just stay here.

954
01:19:00,485 --> 01:19:03,065
Goodness, look at your shoes.
They are drenched.

955
01:19:03,155 --> 01:19:04,405
You are injured.

956
01:19:05,991 --> 01:19:09,491
There is a commotion in the capital.
Some assassins attacked him last night.

957
01:19:10,579 --> 01:19:12,829
-Do not kill him!
-Kill him.

958
01:19:13,790 --> 01:19:15,880
-He is a soul shifter.
-Come on out!

959
01:19:15,959 --> 01:19:17,589
-I will.
-Jang Uk.

960
01:19:17,669 --> 01:19:21,969
I do not think it is right to let a mage
who has barged in here leave so easily.

961
01:19:22,048 --> 01:19:24,128
Once they run wild,
there is no turning back.

962
01:19:24,217 --> 01:19:26,217
They will no longer be humans,
but monsters.

963
01:19:26,303 --> 01:19:28,893
We can also protect
the monsters from this world.

